                                                        span.form-check-sign
                                            td
                                                | Flooded: One year later, assessing what was lost and what was found when a ravaging rain swept through metro Detroit
                                            td.td-actions.text-right
                                                button.btn.btn-info.btn-simple.btn-link(type='button', rel='tooltip', title='Edit Task')
                                                    i.fa.fa-edit
                                                button.btn.btn-danger.btn-simple.btn-link(type='button', rel='tooltip', title='Remove')
                                                    i.fa.fa-times
                                        tr
                                            td
                                                .form-check
                                                    label.form-check-label
                                                        input.form-check-input(type='checkbox', checked='')
